name: UNDISCOURAGEABLE will
description:
No matter the mountains ahead, the adversity faced, the times I’ve fallen and failed, I pause, observe the rear view mirror, and say Thank You! for being relentless, resilient, courageous and always getting back up. 

As babies we accepted without judgement, crawling, getting the hang of it. Two years plus later, barely are able to keep up. 


UNDISCOURAGEABLE will

will to learn
will to grow
will to do
will to give
will to see
will to love

Oh yes, I WILL!
